@startuml
actor Pengguna
participant View
participant Controller
participant Model
participant Database

Pengguna -> View : Akses halaman Login
View --> Pengguna : Tampilkan form Login

Pengguna -> View : Masukkan Email & Password\nKlik tombol Login
View -> Controller : POST /login (email, password)

Controller -> Model : attempt(email, password)
Model -> Database : query user by email
Database --> Model : return user data
Model --> Controller : return validation result

alt Kredensial valid?
    Controller -> Controller : Buat sesi login
    Controller --> View : Redirect ke Dashboard
    View --> Pengguna : Tampilkan Dashboard
else Kredensial tidak valid
    Controller --> View : Redirect back with error
    View --> Pengguna : Tampilkan pesan error (Kredensial salah)
end
@enduml
